                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#嗯…{PLAYERAVATAR#SEXPRO[INFO_MALE_PRONOUN_HE|INFO_FEMALE_PRONOUN_SHE]}对凝光的看法和我不一样。{PLAYERAVATAR#SEXPRO[INFO_MALE_PRONOUN_HE|INFO_FEMALE_PRONOUN_SHE]}觉得，还是那位说话过于直白的「玉衡星」更加可信一些。"
